OL,6,FA "violent and dangerous man" has been
OL,7,Fjailed after he entered a woman's home
OL,8,Fat random and attacked her.
OL,10,FBenjamin Guiver, 35, entered the
OL,11,Fproperty in a Pembrokeshire town on
OL,12,FMay 24 this year after already
OL,13,Fentering other properties the same
OL,14,Fevening, and found his victim asleep
OL,15,Fon the sofa.
OL,17,FShe awoke to find Guiver kneeling by
OL,18,Fher side, asking the intruder who he
OL,19,Fwas, to which he replied "I'm
OL,20,FBenjamin".
