OL,6,FThe victim - who cannot be named for
OL,7,Flegal reasons - ran from the property
OL,8,Fwith no shoes on her feet, only for
OL,9,FGuiver to follow her. He caught up
OL,10,Fwith her, grabbed her by the hair,
OL,11,Fpunched her and hit her face on the
OL,12,Fground. He then dragged her back
OL,13,Finside the house by her hair.
OL,15,FHe went on to punch her, bang her head
OL,16,Fagainst a radiator, sexually assault
OL,17,Fher, and strangle her.
