OL,6,FGuiver, of Heol Glyndwr in Fishguard,
OL,7,Ftold his victim: "I'm going to kill
OL,8,Fyou. Stop screaming or I'm going to
OL,9,Fkill you."
OL,11,FHe then told her to draw the curtains
OL,12,Fso that nobody could see him, repeated
OL,13,Fhis threats about killing her and also
OL,14,Fsaid he was going to rape her "because
OL,15,Fit's people like you who ruin the
OL,16,Funiverse".
