OL,6,FSwansea Crown Court heard that police
OL,7,Fofficers were called to the address
OL,8,Fjust before 10.30pm on 24 May after a
OL,9,Frelative of the victim, who had
OL,10,Farrived at the property, raised the
OL,11,Falarm.
OL,13,FThe relative chased Guiver out of the
OL,14,Fhouse but ended up being assaulted
OL,15,Fhimself as Guiver punched and choked
OL,16,Fhim.
