OL,6,FGuiver was charged with causing
OL,7,Fgrievous bodily harm with intent,
OL,8,Ftrespass with intent to commit a
OL,9,Fsexual offence, assault by penetration
OL,10,Fand intentional strangulation with
OL,11,Fregards to the female victim, and
OL,12,Fassault occasioning actual bodily harm
OL,13,Fand intentional strangulation in
OL,14,Frelation to the male victim.
OL,16,FHe pleaded guilty to all offences at
OL,17,Fan earlier hearing and appeared at
OL,18,FSwansea Crown Court on Thursday, 31
OL,19,FOctober, to be sentenced.
