OL,6,FProsecution barrister Robin Rouch read
OL,7,Fa personal impact statement from the
OL,8,Ffemale victim, in which she said:
OL,9,F"What occurred in my house has ruined
OL,10,Fmy life. I feel constantly lost,
OL,11,Funsafe and on edge.
OL,13,F"I genuinely thought I was going to
OL,14,Fdie. There was a point where the
OL,15,Fdefendant had his hands around my neck
OL,16,Fand I could see the end of my life. I
OL,17,Fhave never experienced something so
OL,18,Fterrifying."
