OL,6,FFollowing the sentencing, Jessie
OL,7,FWalling of the Crown Prosecution
OL,8,FService (CPS) said: "The physical and
OL,9,Fsexual violence inflicted on this
OL,10,Fwoman by a complete stranger in her
OL,11,Fown home was horrific. The strong
OL,12,Fevidence presented by the CPS resulted
OL,13,Fin guilty pleas to very serious
OL,14,Foffences. Both victims have displayed
OL,15,Fenormous bravery, and we hope they
OL,16,Fwill take some comfort from seeing
OL,17,Fthis offender brought to justice for
OL,18,Fhis appalling offences."
